{"tid":372882,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【讓我們成功】我想召集連登的力量","createTime":"2017-08-24T15:35:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-27T15:08:21.000Z","uid":137977,"like":14,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"450e2be55036fe3da242ee927d7ced34558e249c","tid":372882,"uid":137977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T15:35:36.000Z","msg":"今晚洛辛堡對阿積士<br />\n讓我們用意念堅信比數係3:2<br />\n以前啲人話連燈燈咩死咩<br />\n我想今晚 就等我地成功創造歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即使連登仔全部喺同一條船<br />\n我知道只要我地齊心 我地會成功安全上岸<br />\n我不怕千萬人阻擋 只怕自己投降<br />\n就這一次 讓我們 名留青史<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae9f32c8694bae4fa8da2aaa4e161e2ff476142","tid":372882,"uid":137977,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T15:37:33.000Z","msg":"以正評為信念"},{"pid":"c7b817aeed04b04208266ff06b738b1240dd6363","tid":372882,"uid":137977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T15:45:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6059359a6cde9ab8e8880731141f4f3072b4b807","tid":372882,"uid":127099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T15:53:01.000Z","msg":"痾煙了"},{"pid":"7318b4e247a59681cc31430fbe928e3efd1afdcf","tid":372882,"uid":137977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T17:17:59.000Z","msg":"cashed <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83bfe49e10f58ace8ff9b8824dce72ea4db713f6","tid":372882,"uid":16961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T20:33:48.000Z","msg":"3:2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/